Class WebSiminovDatas

  • java.lang.Object
    • siminov.web.model.WebSiminovDatas

  • public class WebSiminovDatas
extends java.lang.Object
    Exposes methods to GET and SET Siminov Web Datas structure. 

    
Example:
        <siminov-web-data>

            <data type="data_type">
                <value type="value_type">value</value>
                <data type="data_type"/>
            </data>

            <data type="data_type" />

        </siminov-web-data>
